A three-server secured and monitored web infrastructure:
- Load Balancer: HAProxy with SSL termination.
- Web Server: Nginx.
- Application Server: Handles logic and interacts with the database.
- Database Cluster: MySQL Primary-Replica.
- Firewalls: Protect all servers.
- Monitoring Clients: Track metrics and logs.
- Domain: www.foobar.com with HTTPS.
